highlights.text: Chann Sitare (From "Oye Makhna") by Ammy Virk, Avvy Sra, and Harmanjeet Singh is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 26 spots at #47.
Karan Aujla has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. Players is the highest at #5.
Duniyaa (From "Luka Chuppi") by Akhil, Dhvani Bhanushali, Abhijit Vaghani, and Bob is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #74.
Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
